All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
AuthToken
Authorization Token for logged-in user.
AuthTokenDAO
Used to access and manipulate entries in the AuthToken table in the database.
ClearRequest
Request object to clear database of all information.
ClearResult
Result object with info about the result from clearing the database.
ClearService
Service to clear data from the database.
Event
Stores the info for various events in a person's life.
EventDAO
Used to access and manipulate entries in the Event table in the database.
FillRequest
Request object to fill the database with ancestral data.
FillResult
Result object with info about filling the database with ancestral data.
FillService
Service to fill database with ancestral data for user.
LoginRequest
Request object to log in a user.
LoginResult
Result object with info about the user login.
LoginService
Service to log a user into the system.
Person
Person object stores the Family History info from a person.
PersonDAO
Used to access and manipulate entries in the Person table in the database.
RegisterRequest
Request object to register a new user.
RegisterResult
Result object with info about the registration of a new user.
RegisterService
Service to register new users.
User
Represents a user of the application.
UserDAO
Used to access and manipulate entries in the User table in the database.
